Subject: RE: [T2] Wheel Bearing Identification

> I recently bought a what was supposed to be a bus rear wheel bearing 
> (211 501 283) for a couple of bucks. 
> Is there a database somewhere which identifies 
> bearing applications by the numbers marked on the bearings, 
> maybe with a cross reference to VW part numbers?


That IS a VW part number. Enter the number, without spaces, in the
"search by part # " field on the left menu bar of my site, and it is
identified as a '64-70 outer rear wheel bearing.

